Design thinking. Solving economic problems. Service design. Service design models. Methods or tools in service design. Development and improvement of services.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to create a comprehensive concept of the nature of design thinking and service design and to provide the necessary knowledge and skills to develop services based on the logic of design thinking.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon the completion of the course the student: 1) know the nature and process of design thinking; 2) be able to apply the logic of design thinking in solving economic problems; 3) understand the nature of service design and connections with design thinking; 4) be able to apply the main service design tools based on the logic of design thinking.
